T02TD2117E:156a-0: @156a ` // 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2117E:156a-1: de nas s'a tstsha gdab pa ni /
T02TD2117E:156a-2: rus pa la las thams cad pa'i sngags kyis brab po //
T02TD2117E:156a-3: de nas lag pa rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya bcas la las thams cad pa'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlab /
T02TD2117E:156a-4: sa rin po che sna lnga'i phye mar bsam /
T02TD2117E:156a-5: de la dri sna tshogs pa sbyar ba'i chus sbrus shing brdung ngo //
T02TD2117E:156a-6: de la rin po che yang bdar ngo //
T02TD2117E:156a-7: de nas 'jim pa'i gong bu la rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgyas reg ge byas la las thams cad pa'i sngags lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas la rin po che'i gong bur gyur par bsam /
T02TD2117E:156a-8: las thams cad pa'i sngags kun la sbyar ro //
T02TD2117E:156a-11: 'debs pa thams cad thabs shes rab zung du 'brel 'bi 'bi zab pa /
T02TD2117E:156a-15: 'od zer gyi 'phro 'du byed pa sprul sku'i don no //
T02TD2117E:156a-16: s'atstsha gdab pa'i rim pa slob dpon sngom pa bzang pos mdzad pa rdzogs so//
